quran[14{c,v,t}:
19,12,Yaa Yahyaa khuzil Kitaaba biquwwatinw wa aatainaahul hukma saiyyaa
19,13,Wa hanaanam mil ladunnaa wa zakaatanw wa kaana taqiyyaa
19,14,Wa barram biwaalidayhi wa lam yakum jabbaaran 'asiyyaa
19,15,Wa salaamun 'alaihi yawma wulida wa yawma yamootu wa yawma yub'asu haiyaa (section 1)
19,16,Wazkur fil Kitaabi Marya; izin tabazat min ahlihaa makaanan shariqyyaa
19,17,Fattakhazat min doonihim hijaaban fa arsalnaaa ilaihaa roohanaa fatamassala lahaa basharan sawiyyaa
19,18,Qaalat inneee a'oozu bir Rahmaani minka in kunta taqiyyaa
19,19,Qaala innamaa ana rasoolu Rabbiki li ahaba laki ghulaaman zakiyyaa
19,20,Qaalat anna yakoonu lee ghulaamunw wa lam yamsasnee bashrunw wa lam aku baghiyyaa
19,21,Qaala kazaaliki qaala Rabbuki huwa 'alaiya yaiyimunw wa linaj 'alahooo Aayatal linnaasi wa rahmatam minnaa; wa kaana amram maqdiyyaa
19,22,Fahamalat hu fantabazat bihee makaanan qasiyyaa
19,23,Fa ajaaa 'ahal makhaadu ilaa jiz'in nakhlati qaalat yaa laitanee mittu qabla haazaa wa kuntu nasyam mansiyyaa
19,24,Fanaadaahaa min tahtihaan allaa tahzanee qad ja'ala Rabbuki tahtaki sariyyaa
19,25,Wa huzzeee ilaiki bijiz 'in nakhlati tusaaqit 'alaiki rutaban janiyyaa
